reviews.review_text: 4-23-84. New Haven Coliseum Worst hiss on a SBD I've evr encountered, and unbabalnced musically.  Guess I'll have to keep looking for that great version of my 7th show.
they don't make concerts like this one any more spaceiest 'spanish jam' evah!  the whole 2nd set is loose jam bliss, fav UJB too
interesting There are some interesting moments, but some lame ones too. Bad/Weird sound, besides the hiss the drums also have this hissy treble thing that makes it hard to listen to.
